title: Clinical Research
additional-note: Volume 8, number 1, dated January 1960, is the issue published earliest that has an active renewal, but might not be the lowest-numbered issue with an active renewal.  The issue dated October 1960, also renewed, is called 'Vol. 7, no. 3 & 8' in its copyright renewal record.
